If the item is being returned for reasons such as Buyer’s Remorse, Accidental Order, Cancellation after ship out (and/or after processed), no longer needed/wanted, etc. Outbound shipping which may have been free originally will be deducted as we pay for shipment while shipping the products to our customers. Please note that there is a restocking fee of 20% Refunds: All returns for refund are subject to a minimum 20% restocking fee. Shipping and handling charges are NOT refundable.
